### Test the Movie Recommendation API

### 1. Get all movies
GET https://localhost:7000/api/movies

### 2. Get popular movies from TMDB
GET https://localhost:7000/api/movies/popular

### 3. Search movies
GET https://localhost:7000/api/movies/search?q=inception

### 4. Get all genres
GET https://localhost:7000/api/genres

### 5. Get all users
GET https://localhost:7000/api/users

### 6. Create a new user
POST https://localhost:7000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User"
}

### 7. Get trending movies
GET https://localhost:7000/api/recommendations/trending

### 8. Get personalized recommendations for user 1
GET https://localhost:7000/api/recommendations/personalized/1

### 9. Get similar movies to movie 1
GET https://localhost:7000/api/recommendations/similar/1

### 10. Rate a movie
POST https://localhost:7000/api/ratings?userId=1&movieId=1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "score": 5,
  "comment": "Amazing movie! One of my favorites."
}

### 11. Get movie ratings
GET https://localhost:7000/api/ratings/movie/1

### 12. Get average rating for a movie
GET https://localhost:7000/api/ratings/average/movie/1
